hich uses Basic Authentication along with SSL Mutual Authentication (HTTP B=
asic &amp; TLS MA)</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.1.4:APIproxyinvokinganprovi=
derendpointthatrequiresTLSMutualAuthentication(TLSMA)">Scenario 1.1.4 : API=
 proxy invoking an provider endpoint that requires TLS Mutual Authenticatio=
n (TLS MA)</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.1.5:APIproxyinvokingantoken=
andserviceendpointexternaltoWestpacviaInternetProxythatrequiresOAuth2(OAuth=
2)">Scenario 1.1.5 : API proxy invoking an token and service endpoint exter=
nal to Westpac via Internet Proxy that requires OAuth2 (OAuth2)</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.1.5.1:Respectingtheexpires_=
invalueofthetoken">Scenario 1.1.5.1: Respecting the expires_in value of the=
