dserviceendpointinternaltoWestpacthatrequiresOAuth2withmultiplescopes(OAuth=
2)">Scenario 1.1.8 : API proxy invoking token and service endpoint internal=
 to Westpac that requires OAuth2 with multiple scopes (OAuth2)</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.1.8.1:Respectingtheexpires_=
