</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-2.WSDLProxies:">2. WSDL Proxies:</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.2.1:WebServiceProxyinvoking=
awebservicethatrequirePasswordDigestasInboundSecurityandPasswordDigestalong=
withSSLasoutboundsecurity(Passworddigest&amp;TLS)">Scenario 1.2.1 : Web Ser=
vice Proxy invoking a web service that require Password Digest as Inbound S=
ecurity and Password Digest along with SSL as outbound security (Password d=
igest &amp; TLS)</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.2.2:WebServiceProxyinvoking=
awebservicethatrequirePasswordDigestasInboundSecurityandPasswordDigestalong=
