en(Cleartextpassword)&amp;TLSMA)">Scenario 1.2.3 : Web Service Proxy invoki=
ng a web service that require Password Digest as Inbound Security and Usern=
ame Token (Clear Text Password) along with TLS mutual Authentication as out=
bound security (Username Token (Cleartext password) &amp; TLS MA)</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.2.4:WebServiceProxyinvoking=
awebservicethatrequirePasswordCleartext(UNT)asInboundSecurityandCleartextPa=
ssword(UNT)alongwithSSLasoutboundsecurity(UNTCleartext&amp;TLS)">Scenario 1=
.2.4 : Web Service Proxy invoking a web service that require Password Clear=
text (UNT) as Inbound Security and Cleartext Password(UNT) along with SSL a=
s outbound security (UNT Cleartext &amp; TLS)</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.2.5:WebServiceProxyinvoking=
awebservicethatrequirePasswordDigestasInboundSecurityandSSLmutualAuthentica=
tionasoutboundsecurity(TLSMA)">Scenario 1.2.5 : Web Service Proxy invoking =
a web service that require Password Digest as Inbound Security and SSL mutu=
al Authentication as outbound security (TLS MA)</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario1.2.6:WebServiceProxyinvoking=
awebservicethatrequirePasswordCleartextasInboundSecurityandSSLmutualAuthent=
icationasoutboundsecurity(TLSMA)">Scenario 1.2.6 : Web Service Proxy invoki=
ng a web service that require Password Cleartext as Inbound Security and SS=
L mutual Authentication as outbound security (TLS MA)</a></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-2.ExternalStaffGateway">2. External S=
taff Gateway</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-3.ExternalPartnerGateway">3. External=
 Partner Gateway</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-1.APIProxies">1. API Proxies</a>
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.1:Partnerproxythatrequire=
sbasicauthenticationasinboundsecurity">Scenario 3.1.1 : Partner proxy that =
requires basic authentication as inbound security</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.2:Partnerproxythatrequire=
sJWTValidationasinboundsecurityusingPINGIDP(staticJWKininventory)">Scenario=
 3.1.2 : Partner proxy that requires JWT Validation as inbound security usi=
ng PING IDP (static JWK in inventory)</a></li>
