th: /provider/base/path</p><p>inboundSecurityPolicy:&nbsp;INBOUND_WS_AUTH_P=
ASSWORD_CLEARTEXT_V1.0</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>---</p><p>backendService:</p><p>&nbsp; basePa=
th: /provider/base/path</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;destinationNetwork: external</p><=
p>inboundSecurityPolicy:&nbsp;INBOUND_WS_AUTH_PASSWORD_CLEARTEXT_V1.0</p><p=
>outboundRoutingPolicy: INTERNAL_INTERNET_PROXY_OUTBOUND_V2.0</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
