<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
backendService:
 basePath: /provider/base/path
inboundSecurityPolicy: INBOUND_AUTH_PARTNER_JWT_VALIDATION_V1.0
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.4:PartnerproxythatrequiresJWTVa=
lidation(usingstaticJWK)fromX-AuthorizationHeaderandBasicAuthenticationasin=
boundsecurity">Scenario&nbsp;3.1.4 : Partner proxy that requires JWT Valida=
tion(using static JWK) from X-Authorization Header and Basic Authentication=
 as inbound security</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>env/default/proxy.yaml</b>
