inboundSecurityPolicy: INBOUND_AUTH_PARTNER_XAUTH_JWT_VALIDATION_V1.0</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.1.5:PartnerproxythatrequiresJWTVa=
lidation(usingstaticJWK)fromX-AuthorizationHeaderthroughtheSIMPLIFIEDPARTNE=
RGATEWAY(OAuth2+TLSonly)">Scenario 3.1.5 : Partner proxy that requires JWT =
Validation(using static JWK) from <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" dat=
a-ref=3D"f1d8ca57-9917-4caa-be49-cffda434403c">X-Authorization</span> Heade=
r through the SIMPLIFIED PARTNER GATEWAY (OAuth 2 + TLS only)</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>env/default/proxy.yaml</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
backendService:
 basePath: /provider/base/path
inboundSecurityPolicy: INBOUND_AUTH_PARTNER_JWT_VALIDATION_V2.0</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-2.WSDLProxies">2. WSDL Proxies&nbsp;</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenario3.2.1:PartnerWSDLproxythatrequiresP=
asswordDigest(UNT)asinboundsecurity">Scenario&nbsp;3.2.1 : Partner WSDL pro=
xy that requires Password Digest&nbsp;(UNT) as inbound security</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>env/default/proxy.yaml</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
backendService:
 basePath: /provider/base/path
inboundSecurityPolicy: INBOUND_WS_AUTH_PASSWORD_DIGEST_V1.0
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-Scenatio3.2.2:PartnerWSDLproxythatrequiredP=
asswordCleartext(UNT)asinboundsecurity">Scenatio&nbsp;3.2.2 : Partner WSDL =
proxy that required Password Cleartext (UNT) as inbound security</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>env/default/proxy.yaml</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
backendService:
 basePath: /provider/base/path
inboundSecurityPolicy: INBOUND_WS_AUTH_PASSWORD_CLEARTEXT_V1.0
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-4.ExternalCustomerGateway">4. External Cust=
omer Gateway</h1>
<p>For all Customer Experience APIs you should configure the user community=
 in the component.yaml file to include customer. This will automatically ap=
ply the customer JWT Authentication policy to your API.</p>
<p>The JWK used to sign the JWTs must be deployed by WDP (for EAM) to enabl=
e validation.</p>
<h1 id=3D"Proxyusecasescenarios-5.ExternalProspectGateway">5. External Pros=
pect Gateway</h1>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<p class=3D"title conf-macro-render">Note</p><span class=3D"aui-icon aui-ic=
on-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">For Cognito IDP, you don't need th=
e separate proxy for the external staff proxies instead the internal API wi=
ll drive the registration for external proxies based on user communities me=
ntioned in component.yaml</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>In case of you want to use the Ping IDP to authenticate the JWT token yo=
u can use below config in your experience API which will override the defau=
lt cognito policy to the ping policy.</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>./proxy-override.yaml</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">---=20
prospect:
  inboundSecurity: INBOUND_AUTH_PROSPECT_JWT_VALIDATION_V1.0
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
